title: No. 7 Spartans use blunder to shock No. 12 Michigan, 27-23
text: > Top News No. 7 Spartans use blunder to shock No. 12 Michigan, 27-23 Michigan punter Blake O'Neill (12) fumbles a flubbed punt against Michigan State in the closing seconds of the second half of an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct 17, 2015 in Ann Arbor, Mich. Michigan State's Jalen Watts-Jackson grabbed the flubbed punt and lumbered 38 yards into the end zone for a touchdown on the final play of the game, giving No. 7 Michigan State a shocking 27-23 win over No. 12 Michigan. (Dale G. Young/Detroit News via AP) DETROIT FREE PRESS OUT; HUFFINGTON POST OUT; MANDATORY CREDIT
